flavor_text_entries.red:
When its huge eyes
light up, it sings
a mysteriously soothing melody
that lulls its
enemies to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
When its huge eyes
light up, it sings
a mysteriously soothing melody
that lulls its
enemies to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Uses its alluring
eyes to enrapture
its foe. It then sings a pleasing
melody that lulls
the foe to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
If it inflates to
SING a lullaby, it
can perform longer and cause sure
drowsiness in its
audience.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Looking into its
cute, round eyes
causes it to sing a relaxing melody,
inducing its
enemies to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It rolls its cute
eyes as it sings a
soothing lullaby. Its gentle song
puts anyone who
hears it to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
JIGGLYPUFF’s vocal chords can freely
adjust the wavelength of its voice.
This POKéMON uses this ability to sing at precisely the right wavelength to
make its foes most drowsy.
flavor_text_entries.sapphire:
When this POKéMON sings, it never
pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle
against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, JIGGLYPUFF cannot
breathe, endangering its life.
flavor_text_entries.emerald:
Nothing can avoid falling asleep hearing a
JIGGLYPUFF’s song. The sound waves of its
singing voice match the brain waves of
someone in a deep sleep.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
It captivates foes with its huge, round
eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing
a soothing melody.
flavor_text_entries.leafgreen:
When its huge eyes waver, it sings a
mysteriously soothing melody that lulls
its enemies to sleep.

flavor_text_entries.omega-ruby:
Jigglypuff’s vocal cords can freely adjust the wavelength of its
voice. This Pokémon uses this ability to sing at precisely the
right wavelength to make its foes most drowsy.
flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
When this Pokémon sings, it never pauses to breathe.
If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily
fall asleep, Jigglypuff cannot breathe, endangering its life.
flavor_text_entries.sun:
It hugely inflates its stomach and sings a
mysterious melody. If you hear this melody,
you’ll become sleepy right away.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
Jigglypuff possess a vocal range that exceeds
12 octaves, but each individual’s singing skill
depends on its own effort.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
Recordings of Jigglypuff’s strange lullabies can
be purchased from department stores. These
CDs can be found near the bedding area.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
The songs they sing are totally different
depending on the region they live in. Some even
sound like they’re shouting!
flavor_text_entries.lets-go-pikachu:
Uses its cute round eyes to enrapture its foe.
It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls
the foe to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.lets-go-eevee:
Uses its cute round eyes to enrapture its foe.
It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls
the foe to sleep.
flavor_text_entries.sword:
Jigglypuff has top-notch lung capacity, even by
comparison to other Pokémon. It won’t stop
singing its lullabies until its foes fall asleep.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
By freely changing the wavelength of its voice,
Jigglypuff sings a mysterious melody sure to
make any listener sleepy.
